text: Rowthulapudi Mandal is one of the 64 mandals in East Godavari District of Andhra Pradesh. As per census 2011, there are 38 villages. == Demographics == Rowthulapudi Mandal has total population of 55,236 as per the Census 2011 out of which 28,050 are males while 27,186 are females. The average Sex Ratio of Rowthulapudi Mandal is 969. The total literacy rate of Rowthulapudi Mandal is 51.11%. The male literacy rate is 50.2% and the female literacy rate is 40.4%. == Towns & Villages == === Villages === #A.
